":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh/docs/faq#需要服务器吗","content":"是的，Mosaic 需要服务器来存储数据、同步和使用 AI 功能。你可以将其部署在任何支持 Docker 的机器上——一台便宜的 VPS 就足够了。"},"359":{"id":"/zh/docs/faq-27","page_id":"/zh/docs/faq","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh/docs/faq#如何开始使用","content":"用 Docker Compose 部署服务端（参见快速开始）"},"360":{"id":"/zh/docs/faq-28","page_id":"/zh/docs/faq","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh/docs/faq#如何开始使用","content":"安装移动端 APK"},"361":{"id":"/zh/docs/faq-29","page_id":"/zh/docs/faq","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh/docs/faq#如何开始使用","content":"在移动应用中连接你的服务器地址"},"362":{"id":"/zh/docs/faq-30","page_id":"/zh/docs/faq","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh/docs/faq#需要-ai-api-密钥吗","content":"AI 功能（自动标签、自动摘要、机器人回复）是可选的。你需要在管理面板中配置 AI 提供者（兼容 OpenAI 或 Anthropic）。不配置 AI 时，所有核心功能正常工作。"},"363":{"id":"/zh/docs/faq-31","page_id":"/zh/docs/faq","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh/docs/faq#服务器最低配置","content":"1 CPU 核心，512MB 内存，10GB 存储"},"364":{"id":"/zh/docs/faq-32","page_id":"/zh/docs/faq","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh/docs/faq#服务器最低配置","content":"Docker 和 Docker Compose"},"365":{"id":"/zh/docs/faq-33","page_id":"/zh/docs/faq","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh/docs/faq#服务器最低配置","content":"支持 PostgreSQL 的环境（pgvector 扩展通过 Docker 自动安装）"},"366":{"id":"/zh/docs/faq-34","page_id":"/zh/docs/faq","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh/docs/faq#数据存储在哪里","content":"在你的自己的服务器上。所有数据（笔记、图片、视频）都保存在你控制的硬件上。存储可以是本地磁盘或 Cloudflare R2（兼容 S3）。"},"367":{"id":"/zh/docs/faq-35","page_id":"/zh/docs/faq","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh/docs/faq#能导出数据吗","content":"API 支持通过标准 REST 端点获取所有笔记、日记和资源。管理面板也提供健康和统计信息。"},"368":{"id":"/zh/docs/faq-36","page_id":"/zh/docs/faq","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh/docs/faq#数据加密吗","content":"**传输中**：是的，通过反向代理配置 HTTPS 后加密（参见部署指南）"},"369":{"id":"/zh/docs/faq-37","page_id":"/zh/docs/faq","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh/docs/faq#数据加密吗","content":"**静态存储**：数据库级别加密取决于你的 PostgreSQL 配置。文件存储按原样保存在磁盘或 R2 上"},"370":{"id":"/zh/docs/faq-38","page_id":"/zh/docs/faq","tags":[],"type":"text","url"